title: KMFDM - Light [1994] EAC FLAC LOG
description:
KMFDM - Light [1994] EAC FLAC LOG

Light is a KMFDM single from their 1993 album Angst. The single was released in 1994 and contains nine different remixes of "Light".

Track listing

   1. "Light (Cellulite Radio Dub by KMFDM)" 3:49
   2. "Light (Aerobic Dub by Excessive Force)" 5:44
   3. "Light (Rubber Gloves Dub by Die Warzau)" 5:24
   4. "Light (Fat Back Dub by Nine Inch Nails)" 7:29
   5. "Light (Vengeance Dub by Son Of A Gun)" 5:39
   6. "Light (Complete Orgasm Dub by Crunch-O-Matic)" 4:58
   7. "Light (Diet Dub by KMFDM)" 5:58
   8. "Light (Lighthouse Dub by Vince Lawrence)" 5:05
   9. "Light (White Cotton Balls Dub by Die Warzau)" 5:09

[edit] Note

    * The vinyl release only contains tracks 2, 3, 4 and 5.
